[
  {
    "id": 5801,
    "number": 1,
    "key": "81:1",
    "textAr": "إِذَا ٱلشَّمْسُ كُوِّرَتْ",
    "textEn": "When the sun is wrapped up [in darkness]",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5802,
    "number": 2,
    "key": "81:2",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ ٱنكَدَرَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when the stars fall, dispersing,",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5803,
    "number": 3,
    "key": "81:3",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلْجِبَالُ سُيِّرَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when the mountains are removed",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5804,
    "number": 4,
    "key": "81:4",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلْعِشَارُ عُطِّلَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when full-term she-camels are neglected",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5805,
    "number": 5,
    "key": "81:5",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلْوُحُوشُ حُشِرَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when the wild beasts are gathered",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5806,
    "number": 6,
    "key": "81:6",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلْبِحَارُ سُجِّرَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when the seas are filled with flame",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5807,
    "number": 7,
    "key": "81:7",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلنُّفُوسُ زُوِّجَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when the souls are paired",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5808,
    "number": 8,
    "key": "81:8",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلْمَوْءُۥدَةُ سُئِلَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when the girl [who was] buried alive is asked",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5809,
    "number": 9,
    "key": "81:9",
    "textAr": "بِأَىِّ ذَنۢبٍ قُتِلَتْ",
    "textEn": "For what sin she was killed",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5810,
    "number": 10,
    "key": "81:10",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلصُّحُفُ نُشِرَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when the pages are spread [i.e., made public]",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5811,
    "number": 11,
    "key": "81:11",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ كُشِطَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when the sky is stripped away",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5812,
    "number": 12,
    "key": "81:12",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلْجَحِيمُ سُعِّرَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when Hellfire is set ablaze",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5813,
    "number": 13,
    "key": "81:13",
    "textAr": "وَإِذَا ٱلْجَنَّةُ أُزْلِفَتْ",
    "textEn": "And when Paradise is brought near,",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5814,
    "number": 14,
    "key": "81:14",
    "textAr": "عَلِمَتْ نَفْسٌ مَّآ أَحْضَرَتْ",
    "textEn": "A soul will [then] know what it has brought [with it].",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5815,
    "number": 15,
    "key": "81:15",
    "textAr": "فَلَآ أُقْسِمُ بِٱلْخُنَّسِ",
    "textEn": "So I swear by the retreating stars -",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5816,
    "number": 16,
    "key": "81:16",
    "textAr": "ٱلْجَوَارِ ٱلْكُنَّسِ",
    "textEn": "Those that run [their courses] and disappear [i.e., set]",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5817,
    "number": 17,
    "key": "81:17",
    "textAr": "وَٱلَّيْلِ إِذَا عَسْعَسَ",
    "textEn": "And by the night as it closes in",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5818,
    "number": 18,
    "key": "81:18",
    "textAr": "وَٱلصُّبْحِ إِذَا تَنَفَّسَ",
    "textEn": "And by the dawn when it breathes [i.e., stirs]",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5819,
    "number": 19,
    "key": "81:19",
    "textAr": "إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوْلُ رَسُولٍ كَرِيمٍ",
    "textEn": "[That] indeed, it [i.e., the Qur’ān] is a word [conveyed by] a noble messenger [i.e., Gabriel]",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5820,
    "number": 20,
    "key": "81:20",
    "textAr": "ذِى قُوَّةٍ عِندَ ذِى ٱلْعَرْشِ مَكِينٍ",
    "textEn": "[Who is] possessed of power and with the Owner of the Throne, secure [in position],",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5821,
    "number": 21,
    "key": "81:21",
    "textAr": "مُّطَاعٍ ثَمَّ أَمِينٍ",
    "textEn": "Obeyed there [in the heavens] and trustworthy.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5822,
    "number": 22,
    "key": "81:22",
    "textAr": "وَمَا صَاحِبُكُم بِمَجْنُونٍ",
    "textEn": "And your companion [i.e., Prophet Muḥammad (ﷺ) ] is not [at all] mad.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5823,
    "number": 23,
    "key": "81:23",
    "textAr": "وَلَقَدْ رَءَاهُ بِٱلْأُفُقِ ٱلْمُبِينِ",
    "textEn": "And he has already seen him [i.e., Gabriel] in the clear horizon.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5824,
    "number": 24,
    "key": "81:24",
    "textAr": "وَمَا هُوَ عَلَى ٱلْغَيْبِ بِضَنِينٍ",
    "textEn": "And he [i.e., Muḥammad (ﷺ)] is not a withholder of [knowledge of] the unseen.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5825,
    "number": 25,
    "key": "81:25",
    "textAr": "وَمَا هُوَ بِقَوْلِ شَيْطَـٰنٍ رَّجِيمٍ",
    "textEn": "And it [i.e., the Qur’ān] is not the word of a devil, expelled [from the heavens].",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5826,
    "number": 26,
    "key": "81:26",
    "textAr": "فَأَيْنَ تَذْهَبُونَ",
    "textEn": "So where are you going?",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5827,
    "number": 27,
    "key": "81:27",
    "textAr": "إِنْ هُوَ إِلَّا ذِكْرٌ لِّلْعَـٰلَمِينَ",
    "textEn": "It is not except a reminder to the worlds",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5828,
    "number": 28,
    "key": "81:28",
    "textAr": "لِمَن شَآءَ مِنكُمْ أَن يَسْتَقِيمَ",
    "textEn": "For whoever wills among you to take a right course.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  },
  {
    "id": 5829,
    "number": 29,
    "key": "81:29",
    "textAr": "وَمَا تَشَآءُونَ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُ رَبُّ ٱلْعَـٰلَمِينَ",
    "textEn": "And you do not will except that Allāh wills - Lord of the worlds.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 586,
    "hizb": 59
  }
]